name: I'm Not Trash Mk.2
description:
You are an apple, mistakenly placed into the junk yard. Make it out and to the grocery store, avoiding piles of trash and glass, before you become completely inedible!

Instructions:

WASD or Arrow Keys -  move your Apple

Space Bar - Jumps

Credits:

Programmers: Jennifer Spofford, Douglas Archibald, Calvin Dao

Artists: Alan Braxton, Ethan Le
